## The Edifice Library — Source of Truth

This project is built on **Edifice**, a shared component & design library. **Check
Edifice first** before building anything. Do not invent new styles, tokens, or
components when one already exists.

Raw GitHub base URL:

```
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/{{GITHUB_OWNER}}/edifice-ui/main/
```

### How to fetch from the library

- **Tokens:** fetch `tokens/<name>.ts` (or the bundle `tokens/index.ts`).
  Never hardcode a color, font size, spacing, radius, or shadow — use a token.
- **Components:** fetch
  `components/web/<category>/<Name>.tsx` (web) or
  `components/mobile/<category>/<Name>.native.tsx` (mobile).
  Categories: `layout`, `ui`, `forms`, `marketing`.
- **Hooks:** fetch `hooks/<useName>.ts`.
- **Utils:** fetch `utils/<name>.ts` (always use `cn` for className merging).
- **Prompts:** fetch `prompts/<task>.md` for scaffolding tasks
  (`new-page`, `new-component`, `mobile-screen`, `code-review`).
- **Config:** extend `config/tailwind.base.ts`, `config/eslint.base.js`,
  `config/prettier.base.js`, `config/tsconfig.base.json`.
- **Architecture:** follow `architecture/*.md` for folder structure, the API
  service layer, error handling, and Next.js conventions.

Workflow: **find it in Edifice → copy/fetch it in → extend if needed.** If
nothing fits, build it following Edifice conventions and consider contributing it
back.

